= SDL_GetWindowFlags =

Get the window flags.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
Uint32 SDL_GetWindowFlags(SDL_Window * window);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''window'''
|the window to query
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns a mask of the [[SDL_WindowFlags]] associated with
<code>window</code>

== Version ==

This function is available since SDL 2.0.0.

